Inside Sales Engineer x 2 (REG/201404/04/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007580
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Apr 24 2014
Job Level
Experienced (Non-Manager)
|
Responsibilities:
Provide timely and accurate application, documentation, quotation and technical support to Local Business Partners (LBP), Regional Sales Managers and other personnel that may need said support in order to meet business goals; to include customer presentations and seminars.
Recommend appropriate integrated pressure control solutions and the preparation of quotations thereof and ensure quotation deadlines are met.
Monitor deliveries and follow up actively on any sales lead to help meet business targets.
Process and facilitate the Warranty claim process to ensure quick turnaround on replacement units or parts.
Build good working relationships with Internal and External customers.
Requirements:
Degree in Engineering, preferably Mechanical Engineering, with 1 to 3 years sales experience in the process control industry.
Excellent written and verbal communication and presentation skills coupled with strong interpersonal and influencing skills.
Must be self-motivated, with sense of urgency and driven for results leading to achievement of organizational objectives.
Demonstrate professionalism and integrity with limited supervision.
Strong analytical and questioning skills coupled with ability to develop and implement strategies.
Team player and able to work with people from all levels in the organization.